headline: TMO Launches Next-Generation Mass Spectrometers: Stock to Gain?
summary: Thermo Fisher debuts two advanced MSs, Orbitrap Astral Zoom and Orbitrap Excedion Pro, to accelerate precision medicine and drug discovery breakthroughs.
